h that I had to use the word idiosyncratic to describe it. This was always how I imagined I’d use my English degree. - Timothy Monbleau \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/dynasty-warriors-origins-level-up-weapons-difficulty-1851776109\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/dynasty-warriors-origins-level-up-weapons-difficulty-1851776109\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"99b87b12d38a2a3a08644bcd9e024680\" data-recommend-id=\"image://99b87b12d38a2a3a08644bcd9e024680\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The protagonist of The First Berserker wears dragon-themed armor while standing on a bridge.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The protagonist of The First Berserker wears dragon-themed armor while standing on a bridge.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/99b87b12d38a2a3a08644bcd9e024680.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/99b87b12d38a2a3a08644bcd9e024680.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/99b87b12d38a2a3a08644bcd9e024680.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The protagonist of The First Berserker wears dragon-themed armor while standing on a bridge.\" data-chomp-id=\"99b87b12d38a2a3a08